title: Dodgers beat Padres 6-2 to gain on Mets for home field (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,015 Dodgers beat Padres 6-2 to gain on Mets for home field (Yahoo Sports) LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Corey Seager's two-run single highlighted a five-run third inning and the Los Angeles Dodgers beat the San Diego Padres 6-2 Friday night to take a half-game lead over the Mets for home-field advantage in their upcoming playoff series.
